Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.13,0:24:58.14,0wrt,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正字迹-童体硬笔字体\fs30\b1\fsp-8\1c96F666\3cA49E63\bord0.2\fs40\frz317.6\pos(617.028,364.914)}青春
